    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dependable, budget-friendly option who isn't concerned with perfection. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small dings consistent with its age, and the interior shows noticeable wear on the upholstery and floor mats. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, though it may eventually need attention for minor leaks and typical high-mileage maintenance. It\u2019s a solid daily driver that performs well for its age but definitely shows its history.",
