      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and is ready for a new home. You really won't find one cleaner than this. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
